related_questions.question: What is an inventory sheet?
related_questions.snippet: A product inventory sheet helps your small business keep track of items you use or sell. Each sheet lists a single product and keeps track of how much of the product is coming into your business and how much is going out. ... If using spreadsheet software, dedicate one sheet in the document to each product.
